    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not even just a \"tough time.\" it's more like the core is gone. i look in the mirror and i don't see a person, i just see a biological machine that's still running because it hasn't been told to stop yet. if the art was the thing that made me real, then without it, what am i actually doing here? it feels like a waste of space.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
